    Search athletes

    search_athletes.Rd

    Search for athletes by name.

    Usage

    search_athletes(family_name, given_name = NULL)

    Arguments

    family_name

    Character. Family name.

    given_name

    Character. First name. Default is NULL.

    Value

    A data.frame. Listing all matches.

    Examples

    search_athletes("boe")
